{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/debut-shopify-theme-how-to-add-swipe-for-product-page-images","result":{"pageContext":{"id":109,"date":"2020-12-05T08:57:55","date_gmt":"2020-12-05T08:57:55","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=109"},"modified":"2021-03-04T07:40:00","modified_gmt":"2021-03-04T07:40:00","slug":"debut-shopify-theme-how-to-add-swipe-for-product-page-images","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/debut-shopify-theme-how-to-add-swipe-for-product-page-images/","title":{"rendered":"Debut Theme: enable swiping to product page images"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Debut theme is, undoubtedly, one of the best themes out there be it paid or free. However it comes with one big flaw complained by many that is its product page lacking a proper swiping functionality to improve the UX of the website. <br><br>In this tutorial I&#8217;ll teach you step-by-step how to implement a swiping functionality for Debut theme. <br><br>There are two options:<br><s>Download the simple version clicking here (live preview) &#8211; password is: 123</s> <strong>(no longer available)</strong><br>Download the <strong>pro version</strong> clicking <a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/debut-theme-slider-pro\">here</a>. (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://debut-theme-slider.myshopify.com/products/blue-silk-tuxedo\" target=\"_blank\">live preview</a>)<br><br>This code snippet creates extra options at the customize page of your theme.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Below, whichever options have <em>(customizable) </em>are options that you&#8217;ll be to enable, disable and/or customize in some way. Complete details can be found clicking here.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are all the current features:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table is-style-stripes\"><table><thead><tr><th class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Features </th><th class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">Pro</th><th class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">Simple</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Swipe featured image</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Swipe thumbnails</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Arrows for thumbnails (customizable)</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Loop thumbnail images (customizable)</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Change featured image whenever a variant changes</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Zoom on hover (customizable)</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Loop featured image (customizable)&nbsp;</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Works with multiple dropdown variants</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Arrows for featured image (customizable)</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Number of thumbnails to show <br>(2, 3, no thumbnails or default)</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Change arrows color<br>(for both thumbnail and featured image)</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">&#8220;Featured product section&#8221; <br>also working with slider</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"> ✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Update dropdown variant whenever image is changed (customizable &#8211; works exclusively with dropdowns. If you&#8217;re using custom swatches or buttons to show variants this function will not work.)</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Frequent updates</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Bug fixes</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">Constantly maintained </td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-left\" data-align=\"left\">New features based on user feedback</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">✔️</td><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\"></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Complete details about the <strong>pro</strong> version can be found <a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/debut-theme-slider-pro\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Making a backup of your theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Before diving into the tutorial make sure you download the theme, so in case you face any issues you can easily revert back.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1514\" height=\"481\" class=\"wp-image-503\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png 1514w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-600x191.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-1200x381.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-768x244.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1514px) 100vw, 1514px\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Getting ready and downloading the code files</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>In your Shopify admin, go to&nbsp;<strong>Online Store</strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Themes&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Actions&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Edit Code</strong>.</li><li>There will be three files inside of the .zip you downloaded: <strong>product-template.txt </strong>, <strong>featured-template.txt </strong>and <strong>theme.txt</strong>. </li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3>Setting up the product-template.txt file</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Open the <strong>product-template.txt </strong>file and copy all the code in there.</li><li>Now go back to your Shopify admin, find the <strong>product-template.liquid</strong> file in your theme.</li><li>Delete everything in there and paste the code that you copied.</li><li>Save. It should look like this:</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"776\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-1200x776.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-110\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-1200x776.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-600x388.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-768x496.png 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image.png 1230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Setting up the theme.txt file</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Now open the downloaded file named <strong>theme.txt</strong> and copy all the code in there.</li><li>In your Shopify theme, find the file <strong>theme.js</strong>.</li><li><strong>Do not delete everything in there</strong>! Instead, scroll all the way down and, at the very bottom of the file, paste the code.</li><li>Click on &#8220;save&#8221;.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"764\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-1-1200x764.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-112\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-1-1200x764.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-1-600x382.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-1-768x489.png 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/image-1.png 1295w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Setting up featured-product.txt (optional)</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In the pro version you&#8217;ll receive an extra file called <strong>featured-product.txt</strong>. It allows you to implement the slider with the section Featured Product in Debut. <strong>Please keep in mind that you can use only one section with it.</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ol id=\"block-f91f6f4c-e07e-4749-bf87-2a50ff0d3845\"><li>Open the downloaded file named <strong>featured-product.txt</strong> and copy all the code in there.</li><li>In your Shopify theme, find the file <strong>featured-product.liquid</strong>.</li><li>Delete everything in there and paste the code that you copied.</li><li>Click on &#8220;save&#8221;.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>That is it! Any questions or concerns? Just reach out to us and we&#8217;ll help you out as soon as possible, typically within 12h.</p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ever wanted to enable &#8220;swiping&#8221; on your Debut theme product images? Now it&#8217;s possible. And it takes less than 2 minutes.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":342,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[154,157],"image_alt":"","acf":[],"featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Debut-Slider-Pro-5-600x338.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Debut-Slider-Pro-5-100x100.png","post_count":8,"categories_names":["Blog"],"tag_names":["Code Tutorial","debut theme"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/109"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/users/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/comments?post=109"}],"version-history":[{"count":10,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/109/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":509,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/109/revisions/509"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media/342"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media?parent=109"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/categories?post=109"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/tags?post=109"